:

1. *Braka* se u današnje vreme često odgađa (The wedding is often postponed nowadays). 
2. *Braku* su prethodili brojni izazovi (Many challenges preceded the wedding). 
3. Njihovoj *braci* nije bilo suđeno (Their wedding was not destined). 
4. Ona nije želela da se uda u *braku* koji joj je nametnut (She didn't want to marry in a marriage that was imposed on her). 
5. Oni su se obeseli i rešili da se ožene u *braku* (They got engaged and decided to marry).